text: Clark Davis (born 15 May 1957 in Calgary) is a Canadian former wrestler who competed in the 1984 Summer Olympics and in the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Calgary Category:Olympic wrestlers of Canada Category:Wrestlers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Canadian male sport wrestlers Category:Commonwealth Games gold medallists for Canada Category:Wrestlers at the 1982 Commonwealth Games Category:Wrestlers at the 1986 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in wrestling Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games medalists in wrestling Category:World Wrestling Championships medalists Category:Wrestlers at the 1979 Pan American Games Category:Medalists at the 1981 Summer Universiade
title: Clark Davis (wrestler)
